{"tid":2224061,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12 歲少女遭警撲倒　呈抗辯信拒交限聚令罰款","createTime":"2020-09-30T09:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T09:26:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9f22c39215d1c6c140d053d700fffd3c58ba0e04","tid":2224061,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"余德寶向《立場新聞》表示，兩兄妹是在 9 月 25 日交罰款限期前，向警方呈交抗辯書，表示不會繳交 9 月 6 日遭票控的罰款。余德寶提到，暫不方便透露抗辯信內容，但抗辯方向大致上是兩兄妹為同住家人，而按照《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集)規例》第 599G 章，共住的同一戶人是獲豁免遵守限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n余德寶表示，兩兄妹提出抗辯，而非交罰款是因認為警方做法不合理，女童母親則不滿警方制服女兒時所用武力。余德寶續說，女童被制服後還遭票控，但她和胞兄當時是沒有意圖與他人聚集，他們只不過是出外購買顏料，所以便要抗辯去反抗警方無理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/12-%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%92%B2%E5%80%92-%E5%91%88%E6%8A%97%E8%BE%AF%E4%BF%A1%E6%8B%92%E4%BA%A4%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F12-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2592%25B2%25E5%2580%2592-%25E5%2591%2588%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%258B%2592%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=6c82d8e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F12-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2592%25B2%25E5%2580%2592-%25E5%2591%2588%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%258B%2592%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%2F&h=c47f983b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/12-%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%92%B2%E5%80%92-%E5%91%88%E6%8A%97%E8%BE%AF%E4%BF%A1%E6%8B%92%E4%BA%A4%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE/</a>"},{"pid":"2791ac24a54c3379db9a5e95062212ab84b993c4","tid":2224